#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Administration Handbook"
msgstr "Administrativni priročnik"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is a rich educational software suite which contains a wide range "
"of activities."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; je bogat paket izobraževalne programske opreme, ki vsebuje širok "
"nabor dejavnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It offers various activities aimed at covering a variety of fields. The "
"topics include reading and typing, arithmetics, geography, sciences, and "
"other topics. It is meant to be used both at home and at school."
msgstr ""
"Ponuja različne dejavnosti, ki pokrivajo različna področja. Teme vključujejo "
"branje in tipkanje, aritmetiko, geografijo, naravoslovje in druge teme. "
"Namenjen je uporabi doma in v šoli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The purpose of &gcompris; is to provide playful activities but always "
"educational."
msgstr ""
"Namen projekta &gcompris; je zagotoviti igrive dejavnosti, ki pa so vedno "
"poučne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is part of &kde; project and is placed under the <ulink url="
"\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html\">AGPLv3 license</ulink>. All "
"the code, except the engine for analog electricity activity is under <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\">GPLv3 license</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; je del projekta &kde; in je pod <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/"
"licenses/agpl-3.0.html\">licenco AGPLv3</ulink>. Vsa koda, razen motorja za "
"analogno električno dejavnost, je pod <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/"
"licenses/gpl.html\">licenco GPLv3</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is available on the following operating systems: &GNU;/&Linux;, "
"&BSD;, &macOS;, &Windows;, Android. It requires a 3D card with support of "
"<emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> or higher. 32 bits color depth is mandatory."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; je na voljo v naslednjih operacijskih sistemih: &GNU;/&Linux;, "
"&BSD;, &macOS;, &Windows;, Android. Zahteva kartico 3D s podporo "
"<emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> ali višjo. 32-bitna barvna globina je "
"obvezna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Namestitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The software is delivered under several forms. Follow the process according "
"to your case."
msgstr ""
"Programska oprema je na voljo v več oblikah. Postopek izvajajte v skladu s "
"svojim primerom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;: use the packages delivered by your &GNU;/&Linux; "
"distribution. If &gcompris; is not packaged in your &Linux; distribution, "
"please contact them to ask for the inclusion of &gcompris;."
msgstr ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;: uporabite pakete, ki jih zagotavlja vaša distribucija &GNU;/"
"&Linux;. Če &gcompris; ni pakiran v vaši distribuciji &Linux;, se obrnite na "
"njih in prosite za vključitev &gcompris;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&Windows;: delivered under a classic installer for &Windows; or via the "
"Microsoft Store."
msgstr ""
"&Windows;: je na voljo s klasičnim namestitvenim programom za &Windows; ali "
"prek trgovine Microsoft Store."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "&macOS;: delivered under a classic installer."
msgstr "&macOS;: dobavljen v klasičnem namestitvenem programu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Android: distributed by the F-Droid store or Google Play Store. APK file is "
"also available."
msgstr ""
"Android: distribuira ga trgovina F-Droid ali trgovina Google Play. Na voljo "
"je tudi datoteka APK."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "The User Interface"
msgstr "Uporabniški vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The interface is designed for easy use by small children. &gcompris; is "
"controlled with a mouse. Keyboard navigation is also available on most of "
"the activities."
msgstr ""
"Vmesnik je zasnovan tako, da ga lahko uporabljajo tudi majhni otroci. "
"&gcompris; upravlja se z miško. Pri večini dejavnosti je na voljo tudi "
"navigacija s tipkovnico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window"
msgstr "Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start the program, &gcompris; shows a graphical interface which "
"presents the list of activities with a control bar at the bottom."
msgstr ""
"Ob zagonu programa &gcompris; se prikaže grafični vmesnik, ki prikazuje "
"seznam dejavnosti z nadzorno vrstico na dnu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here’s a screenshot of &gcompris; main window"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &gcompris; glavno okno"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gcompris; Main Window"
msgstr "&gcompris; Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each icon represents an activity. Around each one, you can find small icons "
"which give additional information about the activity. A simple click on the "
"icon will lead you to an activity or a menu of activities. There are 8 "
"sections (categories) of activities, which are placed on the top or on the "
"left (only if your orientation is portrait). For example, there is section "
"“Board Games”, which includes board games, like Chess, Tic-Tac-Toe or Align "
"Four."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka ikona predstavlja dejavnost. Okrog vsake najdete majhne ikone, ki "
"dajejo dodatne informacije o dejavnosti. Preprost klik na ikono vas pripelje "
"do dejavnosti ali menija dejavnosti. Obstaja 8 razdelkov (kategorij) "
"dejavnosti, ki so postavljeni na vrhu ali na levi (samo če je vaša "
"usmerjenost pokončna). Na primer, obstaja razdelek »Namizne igre«, ki "
"vključuje namizne igre, kot so Šah, Tik-Tak-Toe ali Štiri v vrsto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some categories have subcategories to better filter the activities. For math "
"activities, we have three subcategories: numeration, arithmetic and measures."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere kategorije imajo podkategorije za boljše filtriranje dejavnosti. "
"Pri matematičnih dejavnostih imamo tri podkategorije: štetje, aritmetika in "
"mere."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The stars indicate the age group for which each game is designed:"
msgstr ""
"Z zvezdicami je označena starostna skupina, za katero je posamezna igra "
"namenjena:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "1, 2 or 3 yellow stars — for 2 to 6 years old."
msgstr "1, 2 ali 3 rumene zvezdice - za otroke, stare od 2 do 6 let."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "1, 2 or 3 red stars — greater than 6 years old."
msgstr "1, 2 ali 3 rdeče zvezdice - starejši od 6 let."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the screen there is a control bar for &gcompris;. The "
"possible icons are (the icons are only displayed if they are available in "
"the activity):"
msgstr ""
"Na dnu zaslona je nadzorna vrstica za &gcompris;. Možne so naslednje ikone "
"(ikone so prikazane le, če so na voljo v dejavnosti):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Home — Leaves the current activity, returns to the previous menu."
msgstr "Domov — zapusti trenutno dejavnost in se vrne v prejšnji meni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"“OK” — Validate, confirm your answer. Some activities do not detect "
"automatically whether or not the child has completed the task. In this case, "
"you have to click on this icon. You can also use the &Enter; key on your "
"keyboard."
msgstr ""
"\"V redu\" — Ovrednotite, potrdite svoj odgovor. Nekatere dejavnosti ne "
"zaznajo samodejno, ali je otrok opravil nalogo ali ne. V tem primeru morate "
"klikniti to ikono. Uporabite lahko tudi &Enter; tipko na tipkovnici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Light — Display a hint for the activity. We can help the children on some "
"activities to guide them to find the answers."
msgstr ""
"Svetlo - Prikaže namig za dejavnost. Otrokom lahko pomagamo pri nekaterih "
"dejavnostih in jih usmerjamo pri iskanju odgovorov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Arrows — The present level is displayed. Click on one of the arrows to "
"select another level. Generally, the activities offer several levels whose "
"numbers depend on the activity. In &gcompris;, it is possible to go to the "
"next level without having completed the current level."
msgstr ""
"Puščice — prikazana je trenutna raven. Kliknite eno od puščic, da izberete "
"drugo raven. Na splošno dejavnosti ponujajo več ravni, katerih število je "
"odvisno od dejavnosti. V &gcompris; je mogoče iti na naslednjo raven, ne da "
"bi končali trenutno raven."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lips — Ask &gcompris; to repeat the question."
msgstr "Ustnice - Prosite &gcompris;, naj ponovi vprašanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Question mark — Display the help dialog box. Sometimes, an activity can be "
"too complex to be described easily in the description area. In this case, "
"this function gives access to additional information."
msgstr ""
"Vprašaj — Prikaži pogovorno okno s pomočjo. Včasih je lahko dejavnost preveč "
"zapletena, da bi jo zlahka opisali v območju opisa. V tem primeru ta "
"funkcija omogoča dostop do dodatnih informacij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tool box — Configuration menu. The configuration is saved in the user "
"repository (folder) under the name <filename>.config/gcompris/gcompris-qt."
"conf</filename>. This is a text file which can be edited manually."
msgstr ""
"Orodjarna - Meni konfiguracije. Konfiguracija je shranjena v uporabniški "
"shrambi (mapi) pod imenom <filename>.config/gcompris/gcompris-qt.conf</"
"filename>. To je besedilna datoteka, ki jo lahko urejate ročno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"List item — Display the activity settings menu. There are two possible tabs "
"here. First one, “Dataset”, allows to choose the levels of the activities "
"depending on several objectives and the second one, “Options”, allows to "
"update the configuration of the activity if available."
msgstr ""
"Element seznama — Prikaže meni z nastavitvami dejavnosti. Na voljo sta možna "
"dva zavihka. Prvi, »Nabor podatkov«, omogoča izbiro ravni dejavnosti glede "
"na več ciljev, drugi, »Možnosti«, pa omogoča posodobitev konfiguracije "
"dejavnosti, če je na voljo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Capital “G” — Information box on &gcompris;, presents the main contributors "
"and the version of the software."
msgstr ""
"Velika črka \"G\" - Okno z informacijami o &gcompris; predstavlja glavne "
"sodelavce in različico programske opreme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Power — Quit &gcompris;. You can also use the shortcut on your keyboard "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Napajanje - Zapusti &gcompris;. Uporabite lahko tudi bližnjico na tipkovnici "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kiosk Mode"
msgstr "Način Kiosk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you use &gcompris; with small children or on a self-service kiosk, you "
"can disable a certain number of options:"
msgstr ""
"Če &gcompris; uporabljate z majhnimi otroki ali na samopostrežnem kiosku, "
"lahko onemogočite določeno število možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --enable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"disable the <guiicon>Quit</guiicon> and <guiicon>Configuration</guiicon> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --enable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"onemogoči <guiicon>Izhod</guiicon> in tipki <guiicon>Konfiguracija</guiicon>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --disable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"enable the <guiicon>Quit</guiicon> and <guiicon>Configuration</guiicon> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --disable-kioskmode</command></userinput> : "
"Omogoči <guiicon>Izhod</guiicon> in tipki <guiicon>Konfiguracija</guiicon>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -f</command></userinput>: run &gcompris; in "
"fullscreen mode"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -f</command></userinput> : zažene &gcompris; v "
"celozaslonskem načinu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -C</command></userinput>: disable the cursor "
"(touch screen mode)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -C</command></userinput>: onemogoči kurzor (pri "
"način zaslona na dotik)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "These options can of course be combined."
msgstr "Te možnosti lahko seveda kombinirate."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Bližnjice na tipkovnici"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut"
msgstr "Bližnjica"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Action"
msgstr "Dejanje"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Esc; or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>"
msgstr ""
"&Esc; ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit the current activity or dialog then return to the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Zaključite trenutno dejavnost ali pogovorno okno in se vrnite v glavni meni."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit &gcompris; without further notice."
msgstr "Opustite &gcompris; brez dodatnega obvestila."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle fullscreen mode."
msgstr "Preklopite celozaslonski način."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle sound mute."
msgstr "Preklapljanje izklopa zvoka."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display or hide the control bar."
msgstr "Prikaže ali skrije nadzorno vrstico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notes on Internationalization"
msgstr "Opombe o internacionalizaciji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is internationalized and is available in more than 35 languages. "
"If you want to check if your language is available, you can start &gcompris; "
"and select your language in the option of configuration."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; je internacionaliziran in na voljo v več kot 35 jezikih. Če "
"želite preveriti, ali je vaš jezik na voljo, lahko zaženete program "
"&gcompris; in v možnosti konfiguracije izberete svoj jezik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be careful, some languages need specific fonts to be displayed correctly."
msgstr ""
"Bodite previdni, saj nekateri jeziki za pravilen prikaz potrebujejo posebne "
"pisave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your language is not supported, you can contribute to the software and "
"add the translation of your language. If you are interested, you can contact "
"the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams\">translation team</ulink> of "
"the &kde; project for your language. You can check the level of translation "
"for your language on the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">&kde; "
"translation web site</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če vaš jezik ni podprt, lahko prispevate k programski opremi in dodate "
"prevod svojega jezika. Če vas to zanima, se lahko obrnete na <ulink url="
"\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams\">prevajalsko ekipo</ulink> projekta &kde; za "
"svoj jezik. Stopnjo prevoda za svoj jezik lahko preverite na <ulink url="
"\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">&kde; spletnem mestu s prevodi</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Language learning"
msgstr "Učenje jezikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use &gcompris; in a foreign language that you are learning. Select a "
"foreign language in the configuration menu. Do not forget to download the "
"optional audio modules for this language."
msgstr ""
"V tujem jeziku, ki se ga učite, lahko uporabite &gcompris;. V meniju "
"konfiguracije izberite tuji jezik. Ne pozabite prenesti izbirnih zvočnih "
"modulov za ta jezik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizing activities"
msgstr "Dejavnosti prilagajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can customize some activities using the configuration button in them. "
"For example, you can set the locale in some text activities (like "
"wordsgame), or make it show real car images instead of filled rectangles "
"(traffic)."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere dejavnosti lahko prilagodite z gumbom za konfiguracijo v njih. Na "
"primer, lahko nastavite lokalne nastavitve v nekaterih besedilnih "
"dejavnostih (npr. besedna igra) ali naj prikazuje prave slike avtomobilov "
"namesto zapolnjenih pravokotnikov (promet)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For multiple activities, you can choose several datasets in the "
"configuration. Each one has a specific objective which is described."
msgstr ""
"Pri več dejavnostih lahko v konfiguraciji izberete več podatkovnih nizov. "
"Vsak od njih ima poseben cilj, ki je opisan."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Dataset of activity “Count the items”</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Nabor podatkov dejavnosti \"Preštej elemente\"</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Dataset of activity “Count the items”</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nabor podatkov dejavnosti \"Preštej elemente\"</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can choose the options for this activity."
msgstr "Izberete lahko možnosti za to dejavnost."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select mode of activity “Count the items”</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izberi način dejavnosti \"Preštej predmete\"</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select mode of activity “Count the items”</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izberi način dejavnosti \"Preštej predmete\"</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Console Parameters"
msgstr "Parametri konzole"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Running &gcompris; from a command console with the “--help” option will "
"display all the parameters it accepts:"
msgstr ""
"Če zaženete ukaz &gcompris; iz ukazne konzole z možnostjo “--help”, se "
"prikažejo vsi parametri, ki jih sprejema:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "-f, --fullscreen"
msgstr "-f, --fullscreen"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; in fullscreen mode."
msgstr "Zaženi &gcompris; v celozaslonskem načinu."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "-w, --window"
msgstr "-w, --window"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; in window mode."
msgstr "Zaženi &gcompris; v okenskem načinu."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "-s, --sound"
msgstr "-s, --sound"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; with sound enabled."
msgstr "Zaženi &gcompris; z omogočenim zvokom."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "-m, --mute"
msgstr "-m, --mute"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; without sound."
msgstr "Zaženi &gcompris; brez zvoka."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "-c, --cursor"
msgstr "-c, --cursor"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; with the default system cursor."
msgstr "Zaženi &gcompris; s privzetim sistemskim kurzorjem."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "-C, --nocursor"
msgstr "-C, --nocursor"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; without cursor (touch screen mode)."
msgstr "Zaženi &gcompris; brez kazalca (način zaslona na dotik)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v, --version"
msgstr "-v, --version"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print the version of &gcompris;."
msgstr "Natisni različico &gcompris;."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "-l, --list-activities"
msgstr "-l, --list-activities"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Outputs all the available activities on the standard output."
msgstr "Na standardni izhod izpiše vse razpoložljive dejavnosti."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid "--launch activity"
msgstr "--launch activity"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the activity when starting &gcompris;."
msgstr "Določi dejavnost ob zagonu programa GCompris."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "--start-level level"
msgstr "--start-level raven"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the level on which to start the activity specified by “--launch” "
"option when starting &gcompris;. Ignored if no “--launch” option, or if "
"level specified is invalid."
msgstr ""
"Podajte raven, na kateri želite začeti dejavnost, določeno z možnostjo \"--"
"launch\" pri zagonu &gcompris;. Prezrto, če ni možnosti \"--launch\" ali če "
"je navedena raven neveljavna."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid "--difficulty {value|min-max}"
msgstr "--difficulty {value|min-max}"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the session, force &gcompris; activities difficulty to be either at "
"value or between min and max values. The values must be between 1 and 6, and "
"if the format is min-max, the min value must be lower than the max value. If "
"it is not the case &gcompris; will not start."
msgstr ""
"Za sejo prisilite &gcompris; da je težavnost dejavnosti bodisi na vrednosti "
"bodisi med najmanjšo in največjo vrednostjo. Vrednosti morajo biti med 1 in "
"6, in če je format min-max, najmanjša vrednost mora biti nižja od največje "
"vrednosti. Če ni tako, se &gcompris; ne bo zagnal."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "--export-activities-as-sql"
msgstr "--export-activities-as-sql"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export activities as SQL."
msgstr "Izvoz dejavnosti kot SQL."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "--enable-kioskmode"
msgstr "--enable-kioskmode"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable the kiosk mode (hides Quit and Configuration buttons)."
msgstr "Omogoči kiosk način (skrije gumba Izhod in Konfiguracija)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "--disable-kioskmode"
msgstr "--disable-kioskmode"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable the kiosk mode (default)."
msgstr "Onemogoči način kioska (privzeto)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "--show-home-button"
msgstr "--show-home-button"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the Home button in the bar (default)."
msgstr "Prikaži gumb Domov v vrstici (privzeto)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "--hide-home-button"
msgstr "--hide-home-button"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide the Home button in the bar."
msgstr "Prikaži gumb Domov v vrstici."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "--renderer={renderer}"
msgstr "--renderer={renderer}"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify which graphical renderer to use. On all platforms, “opengl” and "
"software are available. On Windows, you can use “direct3d11” or "
"“direct3d12” (if it was compiled with Qt ≥ 6.6). On &macOS;, you can use "
"“metal”."
msgstr ""
"Določite, kateri grafični upodobilnik želite uporabiti. Na vseh platformah "
"sta na voljo \"opengl\" in software. V sistemu Windows lahko uporabite "
"\"direct3d11\" ali \"direct3d12\" (če je bil preveden s Qt>=6.6). V sistemu "
"&macOS; lahko uporabite \"metal\"."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "--software-renderer"
msgstr "--software-renderer"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use software renderer instead of OpenGL (should work with any graphical "
"card). Deprecated, use “--renderer=software” instead."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite programski upodobilnik namesto openGL (naj bi deloval z vsako "
"grafično kartico). Zastarelo, namesto tega uporabite \"--renderer=software\"."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "--opengl-renderer"
msgstr "--opengl-renderer"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use OpenGL renderer instead of software (faster and more graphical effects "
"but can crash with some graphical cards). Deprecated, use “--"
"renderer=opengl” instead."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite upodobilnik openGL namesto programske opreme (hitrejši in več "
"grafičnih učinkov, vendar se lahko sesuje pri nekaterih grafičnih karticah). "
"Zastarelo, namesto tega uporabite \"--renderer=opengl\"."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "--locale=locale"
msgstr "--locale=locale"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; with the specified locale."
msgstr "Zaženi &gcompris; z določenim lokalnim okoljem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Windows; Example"
msgstr "&Windows; Primer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add these switches in the desktop icon properties. Here is an "
"example that runs &gcompris; in kiosk mode in full screen, without "
"Configuration button and cursor:"
msgstr ""
"Ta stikala lahko dodate v lastnostih ikone namizja. Tukaj je primer, ki "
"izvaja &gcompris; v načinu kiosk v celozaslonskem načinu, brez gumba "
"Konfiguracija in kazalca:"

#. Tag: command
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\"C:\\Program Files\\GCompris-Qt\\bin\\GCompris.exe\" --enable-kioskmode -f -"
"C"
msgstr ""
"\"C:\\Program Files\\GCompris-Qt\\bin\\GCompris.exe\" --enable-kioskmode -f -"
"C"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "&GNU;/&Linux; Example"
msgstr "&GNU;/&Linux; Primer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create an application launcher and configure the command line parameters. "
"Here is an example that runs &gcompris; in kiosk mode in fullscreen, without "
"Configuration button and cursor:"
msgstr ""
"Ustvari zaganjalnik aplikacije in konfigurirajte parametre ukazne vrstice. "
"Tukaj je primer, ki izvaja &gcompris; v načinu kiosk na celotnem zaslonu, "
"brez gumba Konfiguracija in kurzorja:"

#. Tag: command
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "gcompris-qt --enable-kioskmode -f -C"
msgstr "gcompris-qt --enable-kioskmode -f -C"

